    {
      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "MySQL 备忘清单\n==="
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-1",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "本备忘单旨在快速理解 [MySQL](https://mysql.com) 所涉及的主要概念，提供了最常用的SQL语句，供您参考。"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-2",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "入门\n---"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-3",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "介绍",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "MySQL 为关系型数据库(Relational Database Management System)，一个关系型数据库由一个或数个表格组成，如下所示的一个表格"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-4",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "介绍",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "----"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-5",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "介绍",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "    name ▼ 键            ▼ 列(col)\n┌┈┈┈┈┬┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┬┈┈┈┈┈┈┬┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┐\n┆ id ┆ name   ┆ uid  ┆ level ┆  ◀ 表头header\n├┈┈┈┈┼┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┤┈┈┈┈┈┈┤┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┤\n┆  1 ┆ mysql  ┆ 0    ┆ 3     ┆\n├┈┈┈┈┼┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┤┈┈┈┈┈┈┤┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┤\n┆  2 ┆ redis  ┆ 12   ┆ 1     ┆  ◀ 行 row\n└┈┈┈┈┴┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┴┈┈┈┈┈┈┴┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┘\n    redis ▲ 值"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-6",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "介绍",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "----"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-7",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "介绍",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "• `表头(header)` 每一列的名称\n• `列(col)` 具有相同数据类型的数据的集合\n• `行(row)` 每一行用来描述某个人/物的具体信息\n• `值(value)` 行的具体信息，每个值与该列数据类型相同\n• `键(key)` 用来识别某个特定的人/物的方法，有唯一性"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-8",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "登录MySQL",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "# 默认用户名<root>，-p 是密码，\n# ⚠️参数后面不需要空格\nmysql -h 127.0.0.1 -u <用户名> -p<密码>\nmysql -D 数据库名 -h 主机名 -u 用户名 -p\nmysql -h <host> -P <端口号> -u <user> -p [db_name]\nmysql -h <host> -u <user> -p [db_name]"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-9",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "常用的",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "#### 数据库 Database"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-10",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "常用的",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ":-|:-\n:-|:-\n`CREATE DATABASE` db `;` | `创建`数据库\n`SHOW DATABASES;`        | `列出`数据库\n`USE` db`;`              | `切换`到数据库\n`CONNECT` db `;`         | `切换`到数据库\n`DROP DATABASE` db`;`    | `删除`数据库"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-11",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "常用的",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "#### 表 Table"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-12",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "常用的",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ":-|:-\n:-|:-\n`SHOW TABLES;`           | 列出当前数据库的表\n`SHOW FIELDS FROM` t`;`  | 表的列表字段\n`DESC` t`;`              | 显示表格结构\n`SHOW CREATE TABLE`t`;` | 显示创建表sql\n`TRUNCATE TABLE`t`;`    | 删除表中的所有数据\n`DROP TABLE`t`;`        | 删除表格"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-13",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "常用的",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "#### Proccess"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-14",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "常用的",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ":-|:-\n:-|:-\n`show processlist;` | 列出进程\n`kill` pid`;`       | 杀死进程"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-15",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "查看 MySQL 信息",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "# 显示当前mysql的version的各种信息\nmysql> status;\n# 显示当前mysql的version信息\nmysql> select version(); \n# 查看 MySQL 端口号\nmysql> show global variables like 'port';"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-16",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "退出MySQL会话",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql> exit"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-17",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "退出MySQL会话",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "退出 `quit;` 或 `\\q;` 一样的效果"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-18",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "备份特定表"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-19",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p db_name table1 table2 > tables_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-20",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "备份多个数据库"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-21",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p --databases db1 db2 > multi_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-22",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "备份所有数据库"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-23",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p --all-databases > all_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-24",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "备份时压缩"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-25",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p db_name | gzip > db_backup.sql.gz"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-26",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "导出不带架构的数据库"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-27",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p db_name --no-data=true --add-drop-table=false > db.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-28",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "仅导出数据"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-29",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p --no-create-info db_name > only_data.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-30",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "仅导出结构"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-31",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p --no-data db_name > only_schema.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-32",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "导出时忽略某些表"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-33",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysqldump -u user -p db_name --ignore-table=db_name.table1 --ignore-table=db_name.table2 > partial.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-34",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "恢复单个数据库备份"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-35",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql -u user -p db_name < db_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-36",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "恢复多个数据库（带 `--databases` 选项备份的）"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-37",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql -u user -p < multi_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-38",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "恢复所有数据库（使用 `--all-databases` 备份的）"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-39",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql -u user -p < all_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-40",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "从 gzip 压缩的备份恢复"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-41",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "gunzip < db_backup.sql.gz | mysql -u user -p db_name\n\n# 或：\n\nzcat db_backup.sql.gz | mysql -u user -p db_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-42",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "恢复单张表（从 `mysqldump` 单表导出文件）"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-43",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql -u user -p db_name < table1_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-44",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "先创建数据库再导入（如果备份中不包含 CREATE DATABASE）"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-45",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql -u user -p -e \"CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS db_name;\"\n\nmysql -u user -p db_name < db_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-46",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "恢复指定字符集（防止乱码）"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-47",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql --default-character-set=utf8mb4 -u user -p db_name < db_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-48",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "恢复时跳过某些错误（如重复键）"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-49",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql -u user -p --force db_name < db_backup.sql"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-50",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "恢复到远程主机数据库"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro-51",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "恢复备份",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "mysql -h remote_host -u user -p db_name < db_backup.sql"
    },
    {
